[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "着きました！\nまずはここから調べましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00808",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こんな所を？　聞き込みっていうからてっきり\n街の中ですると思ってたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00809",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "街での聞き込みも無論行う。だが、まずは現場だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00810",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "被害者たちは、この辺りで行方不明になったという\n話なんですけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00811",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "この辺りで行方不明つったって……\n砂ばっかりで隠れる場所もないよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00812",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ここで消えるとするなら砂の中か、\n人に連れ去られたか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00813",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "砂の中に埋まっちゃってたら、探すのは大変ですね。\nそれに、もしそうだったら、は、はわわわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00814",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "勝手に青ざめるな。生きている前提で考えろ。\nそうでないと、助けられるものも助けられない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00815",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "あれ？　あそこ、誰かたむろしてるよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00816",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あー……あっちー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00817",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "すみませーん！　そこで何をされているんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00818",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あ？　見て分かんねーのかよ\nなんもしてねーんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00819",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "金もなくなっちまったから店にもいられねえし、\nまた稼がなきゃいけねえや……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00820",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "稼ぐって……まさか良からぬことを\n生業としていますか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00821",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はぁ？　んなわけねーだろ！　なんて失礼な奴だ。\n何様なんだよ。名を名乗れ名を",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00822",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "申し遅れました！　わたくし、諸島同盟監察局の\nタイニー・ロンパイであります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00823",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "うお",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00824",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "同じくエルス・マーティンだ。\n捜査に協力してもらおうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00825",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ひっ……あ、あの「鋼のエルス」様でしたか！\nも、申し訳ございません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00826",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "それで、その稼ぎの当てとはなんだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00827",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アウトローな獣人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ベ、ベスティラの闘技場ですよ。\nこの島では拳で稼げるものですから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_706_036_00828",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "わーお……聞き込みっていうか\nもはや取り調べだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00829",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "名前を聞いたら震えあがるあたり、\n知られた人物だねえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00830",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "「鋼のエルス」っていうのは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00831",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "犯罪者にも同じ監察官にも、意見を曲げずに\n容赦しないことから付けられたあだ名です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00832",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスはとにかく仕事人間で、手が空くと\n自分から別の仕事を探しに行ってしまうほどで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00833",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "はー、やり手なんだね。\n上司からの信頼も厚いんだろうなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00834",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "いや、そいつはどうかな。\nできすぎる部下ってのは煙たがられるもんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00835",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい、実はイェルカさんの言う通りでして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00836",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "上司の皆さんはボスの能力は認めているんですけど、\nボスが出張すると、笑顔になるそうです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00837",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー、聞き込みをする側が情報を与えているように\n私には見えるんだが？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00838",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あっ……！　ボ、ボス、もう聞き込みは終わりで？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00839",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ああ。残念ながら手掛かりはなしだ。\n次の現場に向かうぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00840",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はっ！　承知いたしました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00841",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]